The RSL stands for the radiography scripting language.

Here are a basic rules of correct writing a script file:
	only one instruction in line is allowed
	comments cant be in the same line as commands
	one line cant be longer than 256 chars
	the file paths cant contain spaces
	use double backslash in the file paths
	


